    "headline": "How it works",
    "text": [
      "This pattern provides example of AWS Lambda durable functions written in Java and deployed using AWS SAM",
      "The different patterns demonstrated are chaining, fan-out/fan-in, human interaction, monitoring/polling, timers, error handling with saga compensation, map processing, and sub-orchestration",
